{"tid":2427980,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"地盤工涉非法集結被捕 白衫警：你係曱甴唔使搵律師","createTime":"2021-03-01T08:15:06.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-01T11:48:34.000Z","uid":240362,"like":1,"dislike":30,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"36cbefe7d01750c0e8e8df77cb3462bf90284189","tid":2427980,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-01T08:15:06.000Z","msg":"前年12月有示威者在旺角一帶聚集堵路，並用雷射筆射向警方防線。32歲地盤散工被控當日參與非法集結及藏有攻擊性武器，今於西九龍裁判法院受審。辯方指被告在拘留期間，警方無視他要求會見律師，有白衫警更謂：「你係曱甴，唔使搵律師。」又有警員誘使被告錄下招認供詞。惟作供警員不同意指控。<br />\n<br />\n警員23503供稱，前年11月31日晚上在彌敦道乘車巡邏期間，聽到有人向警車投擲雜物的聲音，下車查看發現近旺角道出口有約250至300名示威者追出，向警方投擲傘、水樽及汽油彈，警方兩次發射催淚煙驅散。至凌晨1時許，警員再到彌敦道近弼街掃蕩，約百名示威者集結、叫口號及堵路，警方曾舉藍旗及作出口頭警告。<br />\n<br />\n當日負責拘捕的警員16698供稱，當晚凌晨1時許，他協助同袍於旺角新填地街453號截停三名男子，包括被告。警員在被告褲袋內搜出一支雷射筆，查問下被告保持緘默。<br />\n<br />\n辯方律師反對控方兩段呈堂錄影，內含為被告疑在誘使下作出的招認內容。辯方指出，被告在羈留室曾兩次向警員16698提出要求見律師及家人，均遭無視，一名白衫警更向被告表示「你係曱甴，唔使搵律師」。被告又曾獲告知「錄影時合作的話，好快就可以離開」。惟警員今否認指控，稱被告當時只要求去洗手間和喝水，並無要求見律師。案件下午續審。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210301/VTMGRNK5V5BCJHNB7XK244VTRY/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210301%2FVTMGRNK5V5BCJHNB7XK244VTRY%2F&d=FWesCxf%2Fx1R8NKF8yEGh3UcTp%2BQsjpNju1TtMRGBB4E%3D&h=f0b16512\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210301%2FVTMGRNK5V5BCJHNB7XK244VTRY%2F&h=b028d085\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210301/VTMGRNK5V5BCJHNB7XK244VTRY/</a>"},{"pid":"39ff7efdb03630f0c7f39c7471a46f1b5c10d12e","tid":2427980,"uid":27122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-01T08:15:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1a8ac38554a783ed0940d4fe16e718e25144b4b9","tid":2427980,"uid":68111,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-01T08:16:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />無要求見律師都講得出"},{"pid":"5b441bd7b1ed8795efa3e9df3274da6992ad7c57","tid":2427980,"uid":11291,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-01T08:17:47.000Z","msg":"黑警做埋法官個位"},{"pid":"e0e36d3fe7beeaf4f77ddb06d5a3737c6ce4c3ad","tid":2427980,"uid":183844,"like":10,"dislike":1,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-01T08:21:29.000Z","msg":"佢講明被告保持緘默<br />\n但係又「表明」唔搵律師<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n咁即係點呀？<br />\n用下腦啦廢閪<br />\n自炒呀？"},{"pid":"97d4ca84162c1e762f01e5952644951c2c79c3c8","tid":2427980,"uid":182197,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-01T09:05:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"671ad2a3c4f9a6e5ab71f9781071a02b1b894721","tid":2427980,"uid":80393,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-01T09:07:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"edb5b4bcfc3e5ed6da74e6ef4287c0cc93d6600d","tid":2427980,"uid":71092,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-01T09:42:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1195960a032db77d213a5d1b47406d1187a81aa0","tid":2427980,"uid":179409,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"1a8ac38554a783ed0940d4fe16e718e25144b4b9","tid":2427980,"uid":68111,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-01T08:16:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/f